          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@VeredillasFM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-[#FF0000] transition-all text-[0.9rem] flex items-center gap-2 group">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-[#FF0000]"><path d="M21.54 6.46a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-1.77-1.77C18.58 4 12 4 12 4s-6.58 0-7.77.69A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.23 6.46C1.53 7.64 1 9.08 1 12s.53 4.36 1.23 5.54a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 1.77 1.77C5.42 20 12 20 12 20s6.58 0 7.77-.69a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 1.77-1.77C22.47 16.36 23 14.92 23 12s-.53-4.36-1.23-5.54zM10 16V8l6 4-6 4z"/></svg>
